						<br/>
						<p>10K is managed by veteran Salesforce MVPs <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nickhamm" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:underline; color:white;">Nick Hamm</a>, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/beckymwebster" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:underline; color:white;">Becky Webster</a>, and <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/matthewlamb" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:underline; color:white;">Matthew Lamb</a>, each having 10+ years experience in the Salesforce ecosystem.</p>
						<br/>
						<p>10K Advisors is headquartered in Louisville, Kentucky.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</apex:define>
        <apex:define name="footer">
            <c:X10KViewFooter />
        </apex:define>
    </apex:composition>
    <site:googleAnalyticsTracking />
</apex:page>